[{"type":"message","user":"UJ53U1A9Y","text":"ALEとかが使っている、画面左横にアイコンや文字などを出す機能ってなんて名前でしたっけ...?あのラインを常時出ているようにしたいのだけど設定が思い出せなくて名前も思い出せないのでhelp引けない...","ts":"1558850185.059100","bot_id":"BJKCQJ7D5","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"a817efc6-52e0-406a-842e-70aa9f7eb529","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"ALE が使ってるのは sign ですね。ただあの左の幅自体の名称は foldcolumn だと思います","ts":"1558850424.060000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"8a8473fd-5de5-40b6-ae04-28b430b055c2","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":":h sign","ts":"1558850454.060500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U894RTUJY","text":"```\n2. コマンド                                     *sign-commands* *:sig* *:sign*\n \n次の例ではカレントファイルの23行目に \"piet\" という目印を置いている。目印は \"&gt;&gt;\"\nという文字をともなって表示される。  \n        :sign define piet text=&gt;&gt; texthl=Search\n        :exe \":sign place 2 line=23 name=piet file=\" . expand(\"%:p\")\n \nそれをもう一度消すコマンドを追記しておく:  \n        :sign unplace 2\n \n\":sign\" コマンドの後には他のコマンドを続けられないことに注意すること。そのよう\nにするには|:execute|を使う。\n```","ts":"1558850454.060600","bot_id":"B894RTUCU","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"a7081d0c-552d-4f4d-9f6e-11bc8c21df0d","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":":h foldcolumn","ts":"1558850457.060800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"U894RTUJY","text":"```\n                                                *'foldcolumn'* *'fdc'*\n'foldcolumn' 'fdc'      数値 (既定では 0)\n                        ウィンドウについてローカル\n                        {Vi にはない}\n                        {Vimが |+folding| 機能付きでコンパイルされたときのみ\n                        有効}\n        非0 に設定されると、ウィンドウの端の指定された幅の列が折り畳みを (開い\n        ていても閉じていても) 表示する。最大値は 12 である。\n        |folding| を参照。\n```","ts":"1558850458.060900","bot_id":"B894RTUCU","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"51f4f133-4dab-42a9-aa1c-add2b686112c","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"sign → foldcolumn に画像とか文字を出す機能ってイメージ…？（間違ってたら教えて下さい…）","ts":"1558850531.061500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"5d0c8c40-71a2-4594-b1cc-ced1367bf16b","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"ちなみに foldcolumn は `:diffthis` とかで diff モード有効の場合も表示されます","ts":"1558850671.062100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"7c2a881e-b13d-4686-a807-6d7be067d899","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"いや、隣接してますが、ちょっと違いますね、foldcolumの領域、signの領域、numberの領域が並んでいて、同じではない、と思います。","ts":"1558851107.063100","thread_ts":"1558851107.063100","reply_count":1,"replies":[{"user":"U0M7GCBPD","ts":"1558851707.064600"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"UJ53U1A9Y","text":"signぽいですね。","ts":"1558851174.063200","bot_id":"BJKCQJ7D5","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"fcf9a62f-dc1a-4e91-b215-ad5240ba9046","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"<https://gyazo.com/06413383dcb79f954283ee2e347e3acb>","ts":"1558851198.063400","attachments":[{"fallback":"Gyazo Photo: ","id":1,"title_link":"https://gyazo.com/06413383dcb79f954283ee2e347e3acb","image_url":"https://i.gyazo.com/06413383dcb79f954283ee2e347e3acb.png","blocks":null,"service_name":"Gyazo","service_icon":"https://gyazo.com/favicon.ico","from_ur